statements: SELECT * FROM ProteinInteractionNetwork WHERE protein_id = 1;
SELECT protein_id, interaction_partner_id FROM ProteinInteractionNetwork WHERE interaction_type = 'binding';
SELECT protein_id, interaction_strength FROM ProteinInteractionNetwork WHERE interaction_strength > 0.5;
SELECT * FROM ProteinInteractionNetwork ORDER BY protein_id DESC;
SELECT interaction_partner_id, interaction_type FROM ProteinInteractionNetwork WHERE protein_id IN (2, 4, 6);
SELECT * FROM ProteinInteractionNetwork WHERE interaction_type = 'binding' ORDER BY interaction_strength DESC;
SELECT protein_id, interaction_partner_id FROM ProteinInteractionNetwork WHERE interaction_strength > 0.5;
SELECT interaction_partner_id, COUNT(protein_id) AS interaction_count FROM ProteinInteractionNetwork GROUP BY interaction_partner_id;
SELECT protein_id, interaction_partner_id, interaction_strength FROM ProteinInteractionNetwork WHERE protein_id IN (1, 3, 5) AND interaction_strength > 0.3;
SELECT DISTINCT interaction_type FROM ProteinInteractionNetwork WHERE interaction_strength > 0.7;
SELECT * FROM ProteinInteractions
SELECT protein1, interaction_type FROM ProteinInteractions WHERE interaction_type = 'binding'
SELECT protein_name, gene_symbol FROM ProteinAnnotations WHERE gene_symbol IS NOT NULL
SELECT protein1, protein2, interaction_score FROM ProteinInteractions ORDER BY interaction_score DESC
SELECT protein_name AS name, protein_function AS function FROM ProteinAnnotations
SELECT * FROM ProteinInteractions ORDER BY interaction_id DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT protein1, interaction_score FROM ProteinInteractions WHERE interaction_score > 0.5 ORDER BY interaction_score DESC;
SELECT protein_name, gene_symbol FROM ProteinAnnotations WHERE protein_function LIKE '%transport%' ORDER BY protein_name ASC;
SELECT protein1, protein2, interaction_type, interaction_score FROM ProteinInteractions WHERE protein1 = 'ACTB' OR protein2 = 'ACTB';
SELECT protein_name, gene_symbol, protein_function FROM ProteinAnnotations WHERE gene_symbol IS NOT NULL ORDER BY gene_symbol, protein_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM protein_interactions;
SELECT protein1_id, interaction_type FROM protein_interactions WHERE interaction_score > 0.5;
SELECT protein_name, gene_name FROM proteins ORDER BY molecular_weight DESC;
SELECT * FROM interaction_annotations WHERE annotation_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT protein_name, function FROM proteins WHERE gene_name = 'ABC' OR gene_name = 'XYZ';
SELECT * FROM protein_interactions WHERE interaction_type = 'physical';
SELECT protein1_id, protein2_id, interaction_score FROM protein_interactions WHERE interaction_type = 'chemical' ORDER BY interaction_score DESC;
SELECT * FROM proteins WHERE function LIKE '%kinase%' AND molecular_weight > 60;
SELECT protein_name, function FROM proteins ORDER BY protein_name ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT interaction_id, annotation, publication_id FROM interaction_annotations WHERE annotation_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM protein_interaction_network;
SELECT protein_id, protein_name, interaction_partner_id, interaction_strength FROM protein_interaction_network ORDER BY interaction_strength DESC;
SELECT protein_name, interaction_partner_id FROM protein_interaction_network WHERE interaction_strength > 0.5;

SELECT protein_name, interaction_partner_id, interaction_partner.partner_name FROM protein_interaction_network INNER JOIN protein_interaction_partner ON protein_interaction_network.interaction_partner_id = protein_interaction_partner.partner_id;

SELECT analysis_id, protein_name, partner_name, interaction_type FROM interaction_analysis INNER JOIN protein_interaction_network ON interaction_analysis.protein_id = protein_interaction_network.protein_id INNER JOIN protein_interaction_partner ON interaction_analysis.partner_id = protein_interaction_partner.partner_id INNER JOIN protein_interaction_type ON interaction_analysis.type_id = protein_interaction_type.type_id ORDER BY analysis_date DESC;
SELECT protein_name, interaction_strength FROM protein_interaction_network WHERE interaction_strength >= 0.8 ORDER BY interaction_strength DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT partner_name, interaction_count FROM protein_interaction_partner WHERE interaction_count > 100 ORDER BY interaction_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM protein_interaction_type WHERE type_id IN (1, 3, 5) ORDER BY type_id;
SELECT protein_name, interaction_partner_id FROM protein_interaction_network WHERE interaction_strength BETWEEN 0.5 AND 0.7 ORDER BY protein_name ASC, interaction_strength DESC;

SELECT analysis_date, protein_name, partner_name, interaction_type FROM interaction_analysis JOIN protein_interaction_network ON interaction_analysis.protein_id = protein_interaction_network.protein_id JOIN protein_interaction_partner ON interaction_analysis.partner_id = protein_interaction_partner.partner_id JOIN protein_interaction_type ON interaction_analysis.type_id = protein_interaction_type.type_id ORDER BY analysis_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM ProteinInteractionNetwork LIMIT 5;
SELECT protein1_name, protein2_name, interaction_type FROM ProteinInteractionNetwork WHERE interaction_type='binding';
SELECT protein_name, localization FROM ProteinLocalization ORDER BY protein_name DESC;
SELECT protein_name, structure_file FROM ProteinStructure WHERE id=3;
SELECT method_name, description FROM ExperimentalMethods;
SELECT * FROM ProteinInteractionNetwork ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT DISTINCT protein1_name, interaction_type FROM ProteinInteractionNetwork WHERE interaction_type = 'Binding';
SELECT protein_name, localization FROM ProteinLocalization WHERE localization IN ('Nucleus', 'Cytoplasm') ORDER BY localization ASC, protein_name DESC;
SELECT protein_name, structure_file FROM ProteinStructure WHERE LENGTH(structure_file) > 0 LIMIT 3;
SELECT * FROM InteractionEvidence JOIN ProteinInteractionNetwork ON InteractionEvidence.interaction_id = ProteinInteractionNetwork.id WHERE LENGTH(evidence_text) > 100 ORDER BY id ASC LIMIT 5;
